      "text": [
        " حَصِّنُوا أَمْوَالَكُمْ بِالزَّكَاةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Hassan, from Musa Bin Bakr, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan Musa<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Fortify you wealth with the Zakat’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ali ibn Hassan from Musa ibn Bakr who has said the following: “Abu al-Hassan, Musa, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Fortify your belongings by paying zakat.’” "
        ]
      }
